Texts.Eng:
The Scyphojel are bioluminescent, gelatinous jellyfish that have been at home in the vacuum of space for as long as they can remember. They levitate through the air using energy from the bright spots on the ends of their tentacles. A strange metabolic process allows them to produce electricity from metal.

  ^orange;Diet^reset;: Omnivore, prefers robot food.

